<dl id="n12134k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12134k">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12134k"> 134(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> a latere <font face="wake">+</font>i <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n12134k"><li>FW 177.19 </li><li><a href="../../flex/g/lexg.htm#n12134k">2010</a> </li><li><a href="../../flex/g/l39g.htm#n12134k">1939</a> </li><li><ms href="#n12134k">MS BL 47474-28</ms> </li><li>JJA 47:409 <a name="gd3" href="../../FF/fdra/gda.htm#gd3">Usage</a> </li><li> <a href="../../flex/g/gd3.htm#n12134k">Draft: I.7&sect;1.3</a>/2.3</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">Beno&icirc;t XIII en ces tristes circonstances e&ucirc;t bien voulu s&apos;assurer encore le concours de ma&icirc;tre Vincent. Il fit tout pour le retenir. Vincent, para&icirc;t-il, refusa le chapeau de cardinal. Le pape le laissa donc aller. Mais il eut la supr&ecirc;me habilet&eacute; de donner &agrave;cet apostolat que le ma&icirc;tre allait entreprendre, un caract&egrave;re officiel. Il l&apos;institua l&eacute;gat <mark><i>a latere Christi</i></mark>. <br><font color="green">[Benedict XIII in these sad circumstances would have liked to be assured of the further co-operation of master Vincent. He did everything to keep him. Vincent, apparently, refused the cardinal&apos;s hat. The pope then let him go. But he had the supreme dexterity to give to this ministry that the master was about to undertake an official character. He made him a legate <i><mark>a latere Christi</mark></i> [from the side of Christ]</font>. <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 68</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: See <a name="n04152g" href="n04all.htm#n04152g">N04 (VI.B.25):152(g)</a>. L. <i>A latere Christi</i>: from the side of Christ. Vincent Ferrer was appointed legate <i>a latere Christi</i> by Pope Benedict XIII.</mm> </dd></dl>
